        ],
        "management": "Volume expansion with 5% albumin. Vasoconstrictors: terlipressin 1-2 mg IV q4-6h (or noradrenaline if terlipressin unavailable). Midodrine + octreotide + albumin. TIPS in selected patients. Liver transplant evaluation."
