          { "feature": "diuretic_resistance", "weight": 3 },
          { "feature": "elevated_jvp", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Optimize heart failure therapy. Diuretics (consider ultrafiltration if resistant). Avoid NSAIDs. ACEi/ARB continuation if tolerated. SGLT2i in stabilized patients. Vasodilators if hypertensive."
